40|$|It's {{possible}} to accept or to reject a promise. <b>According</b> <b>to</b> a new proposal by Abraham Roth, accepting a promise involves intending that the promisee perform the promised action. <b>According</b> <b>to</b> Roth, <b>this</b> <b>view</b> {{is supported by}} rational symmetries between promissory acceptance and intention. Here, I show how these symmetries actually generate two problems for the view...|$|R
